<br>
I'd say the magician is the warrior class of the casters.  A magicians strength is lining up toe to toe with one mob and fighting it out.  No Kiting involved.  No Fearing and hitting its back.  Just line up face to face and take it down.  We are rather limited in escape routes (Gate is pretty much our only defensive spell, no root, no stun, no fear, no Feign Death, etc).  <br>
<br>
A lot of strategy goes into setting up the solo fight but after the fight begins you generally have only one objective and thats to kill the mob quickly as adds are a lot of trouble.<br>
<br>
Anyhow I hope this gives you a little just on the view of a magician as a soloist as opposed to the other classes. <p><br>
